"They are imbibed with the agrarian utopian ideology of the regime."
"They were raised in a business environment is a foreign concept."
Sor Lim, 55, who joined the Khmer red as a teenager in 1974, fought in the jungle around Anlong Veng before settling in 1998 as a poor rice grower.
